sql_explorer:rag_example_queries.question: Who are the top five operators names and what is their daily average rate of picks in last 90 days?
sql_explorer:rag_example_queries.sql_query: select  operator_name , round(count(*)/90) as operator_count FROM `gold_pick` where date(event_timestamp_utc) >=  date_sub(current_date(), INTERVAL 90 day) and  date(event_timestamp_utc) <  current_date() group by operator_name order by round(count(*)/90) desc limit 5;

sql_explorer:rag_example_queries.question: How many operators have been working in last 1 month?
sql_explorer:rag_example_queries.sql_query: select count(distinct operator_name) as operator_count FROM `gold_pick` where date(event_timestamp_utc) >=  date_sub(current_date(), INTERVAL 1 month) and  date(event_timestamp_utc) <  current_date() ;

sql_explorer:rag_example_queries.question: Who are the top 5 best operators in last year based on the number of orders?
sql_explorer:rag_example_queries.sql_query: select  operator_name, COUNT(DISTINCT pick_task_code) AS activePickOrders FROM `gold_pick` where  date(event_timestamp_utc) >= DATE_SUB (CURRENT_DATE(),INTERVAL 1 year) group by operator_name order by COUNT(DISTINCT pick_task_code) desc limit 5;
